ATP's signing model draws on patterns from W3C Verifiable Credentials,
JSON Web Signatures (RFC 7515), JSON Web Key (RFC 7517), and JSON
Canonicalization Scheme (RFC 8785). These are referenced for attribution
only and are not distributed with this work.

ATP's Policy Enforcement Point model draws on patterns demonstrated by
NVIDIA NemoClaw (https://github.com/NVIDIA/NemoClaw), licensed Apache 2.0.
